{"Id":489,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-muhammadmakin","Author":"Muhammad Makin","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://quranenc.com/check/chinese_makin/v1.0.0-csv.1 , https://quranenc.com/en/browse/chinese_makin , https://quranenc.com ,","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":76,"VerseNumber":26,"Text":"夜里，你应当以小部份时间向他叩头，以大部份时间赞颂他。"},{"SurahNumber":76,"VerseNumber":27,"Text":"这等人的确是爱好现世，而忽视未来的严重的一日"},{"SurahNumber":76,"VerseNumber":28,"Text":"我创造了他们，并使他们的体格坚实。如果我意欲，我将以像他们一样的人代替他们。"},{"SurahNumber":76,"VerseNumber":29,"Text":"这确是教诲，谁愿意觉悟，谁可以选择一条通达他的主的道路。"},{"SurahNumber":76,"VerseNumber":30,"Text":"除安拉意欲外，你们决不意欲。安拉是全知的，是至睿的。"},{"SurahNumber":76,"VerseNumber":31,"Text":"他使他所意欲的人，入在他的慈恩中。至于不义的人，他已为他们预备了痛苦的刑罚。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"誓以奉派传达佳音，"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"遂猛烈吹动者，"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"誓以传播各物，"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"而使之分散，"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"乃传授教训者，"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"誓以示原谅或警告者，"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"警告你们的事，是必定发生的。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"当星宿黯淡的时候，"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"当天体破裂的时候，"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"当山峦飞扬的时候，"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"当众使者被定期召集的时候，"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"期限在哪日呢？"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"在判决之日。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"你怎能知道判决之日，是什么？"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"在那日，伤哉否认真理的人们。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"难道我没有毁灭先民吗？"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"然后，我使后民随他们而消灭。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"我将这样处治犯罪的人。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"在那日，伤哉否认真理的人们。"}]}